releases.body:
- Support syntax highlight in code block
- Fix error when opening local markdown: fixes #21

- Add screenshot to README
- Truncate body padding
- Fix a bug that local image wasn't rendered
- Add support for rendering local images.

- Enable to run from terminal in MacOSX.
- Update [electron](https://github.com/atom/electron) to v0.30.4.
